org.alienideology.jcord.handle.managers

Interface ISelfManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SelfManager

    public interface ISelfManager
    ISelfManager - A manager that manages self user. This managers is for both bot and client, which means setting email or password is not supported.
    Author:
    AlienIdeology

      • setStatus

        ISelfManager setStatus(OnlineStatus status)
        Set the online status of this user. Setting the status to OnlineStatus.OFFLINE or OnlineStatus.UNKNOWN will automatically be recognized as OnlineStatus.INVISIBLE. Setting the status to OnlineStatus.STREAMING will be recognized as OnlineStatus.ONLINE.
        Parameters:
        status - The online status.
        Returns:
        ISelfManager for chaining.

      • setPlaying

        ISelfManager setPlaying(java.lang.String name)
        Set the playing status. Use empty or null name to reset the playing game.
        Parameters:
        name - The game's name.
        Returns:
        ISelfManager for chaining.
